{"tid":673096,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★郭思治：我就嚟攞綜援！","createTime":"2018-05-21T14:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T15:37:07.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"52f7cfc4fa1e0a45ef7477cadc7b2239fd879776","tid":673096,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/220609_812749e1a307f38fd0a88b54bea55ff2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F220609_812749e1a307f38fd0a88b54bea55ff2.png&h=62ab55d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日股價暴瀉的民眾金融（279），今日再跌逾兩成至0.1元，其持股8%的中國全通（633），股價亦暴跌近六成至0.72。民眾證券董事總經理郭思治出席東方資本餐飲俱樂部發佈會時表示，最重要是公司運作正常。他續指，民眾金融仍然正常運作，民眾證券亦繼續做生意，「無受影響」。<br />\n<br />\n對於股價下跌，郭思治指難以估計，他表示，「公司一切都係正常，直到而家呢一分鐘，未來一段時期，個運作都仍然保持正常&hellip;&hellip;作為管理層來講，最重要就係公司運作正常，反而你買一隻股票贏定輸，我覺得唔係咁重要，喺我個角度來講。」<br />\n他續指，「如果你以今日收市價1毫子，如果你一路揸落嚟，帳面上虧蝕好多」。他補充，細價股的投機性較重，「風險管理真係要做到足」，「總之買完之後唔對板，我都係減持或者止蝕」。<br />\n他表示，因為股價持續下跌，他作為保守的投資者，會嚴格執行風險管理。對於民眾金融及中國全通兩隻股份，他稱，現時並未持有該兩隻股，「我暫時兩隻都唔會揀住」。他續指，沽貨是在最近一週發生，「幾時沽我諗已經唔重要，總之都係輸錢」，虧損金額方面，他笑稱「都係少少錢啦，<span style=\"color: red;\">就嚟攞綜援</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180521/58221001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180521%2F58221001&d=06Ej3lOb8dMH8tBioTijCwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=6c2df407\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180521%2F58221001&h=65df5001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180521/58221001</a>"},{"pid":"b0e83f6c32786d795530a6f43f4fab72b1e0412f","tid":673096,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:07:09.000Z","msg":"join綜援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0a0f615384979ab08baaf4424903848d5a03ec","tid":673096,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:07:55.000Z","msg":"綜援 is the best<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de81186ab6fb616e4ed130ec6997208f83712aa6","tid":673096,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0e83f6c32786d795530a6f43f4fab72b1e0412f","tid":673096,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:07:09.000Z","msg":"join綜援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:08:44.000Z","msg":"住M記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dbf63934d35a44a1af52d834896c7e5da01d3b8","tid":673096,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:09:47.000Z","msg":"大戶就係跟你「總之買完之後唔對板，我都係減持或者止蝕」, 而家個價咪殘晒囉"},{"pid":"5551864e7fb3fee0ccb5005361bb5abf25d44fce","tid":673096,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:10:24.000Z","msg":"食飽"},{"pid":"b02a9296278405a9a405916eddbe49af571ccee6","tid":673096,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180304/s00001/536041410e340c1875bc62255d6d7a8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180304%2Fs00001%2F536041410e340c1875bc62255d6d7a8c.jpg&h=143db14d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c0b33c5ea10e1a50a6b84370efdf5612457ebd9","tid":673096,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:19:14.000Z","msg":"0.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ad92febe82e1c85650d5468d91e502f23362be","tid":673096,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:21:59.000Z","